00:00:00.780 --> 00:00:03.599
Everyone likes to travel and explore new places.

00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:07.200
And every time we go to a new place,
we face the same questions:

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:09.880
Where do we go? What do we see?

00:00:09.880 --> 00:00:12.400
Who will tell us all these fantastic things?

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:15.699
WHERE M I is here to help you!

00:00:15.699 --> 00:00:17.199
But how?

00:00:17.199 --> 00:00:18.500
Well it's really simple.

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:25.800
Thousands of local people tell their friends
exciting stories about their cities, their history,
and their culture.

00:00:25.800 --> 00:00:31.000
And then there are the visitors, who want to share
own new experiences away from home.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.979
Now all this stories can be turned into tours
multimedia

00:00:33.979 --> 00:00:37.769
using WHERE M I the free storytelling platform.

00:00:37.770 --> 00:00:43.200
Everyone can create and share internal and external
tours, worldwide.

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:45.920
Of course, professionals also use it.

00:00:45.920 --> 00:00:49.530
Museums use WHERE M I for development and sharing

00:00:49.530 --> 00:00:51.539
audio guides that complete the city walks.

00:00:51.539 --> 00:00:54.899
So when you arrive in a new place you will not make
it anymore these questions..

00:00:54.899 --> 00:00:58.000
So get out! Explore and share.